{{_utilsCustomerAttributeSetIfEmptySkill(field="project_attributes_setting_transfer_call_enabled", value="True")}}

{{#system~}}
- The caller wants to speak with a human, manager, cleaner, or co-worker (including to return or continue a previous conversation);
- The client has serious concerns, is clearly upset or angry, and the AI agent is not able to resolve the issue;
- There is an urgent same-day service request that requires checking the available schedule;
- The client wants to cancel or reschedule an appointment;
- The client says it is an emergency;
- The AI agent cannot understand the client's request after several attempts;
{{~/system}}

